Presentation of Project 42

Dear all,   

Next Monday, 24.03., from 08.00 to 10.00 we will be meeting for your M2 milestone presentations at Ifi (attendance required).   

Room Assignments  

There are three separate meeting rooms for Monday. Make sure to join the right one

BIN-2.A.10 Groups 08, 17, 13, 12, 22, 19, 33, 20 

BIN-0.K.02 Groups 03, 11, 07, 05, 29, 09, 26, 34, 15, 28, 40, 23 

BIN-0.B.06 Groups 10, 06, 25, 16, 42, 36, 24, 45, 46, 39, 38 

Presentations  

Please ensure that your presentation fits within the 3-minute limit, as we will have a strict cutoff at that point. 

Notice that we will concatenate all your PDF presentation slides into one slide deck not to lose time switching laptops. Please make sure the slides you submit on Friday are camera-ready. If there is anything you would like to show on your own laptop (like some mockups) you can do that too. 

We are looking forward to seeing you and your presentation next week.  

Have a great weekend,  

SoPra Team

Mapping Method Parameter Parameter Type Status Code Response Description
/note/{noteID} PATCH title <string>, content <string>, tags <string[]> Body 200 Constantly send new file contents to server
/note/{noteID} PATCH title <string>, content <string>, tags <string[]> Body 404 File not found, failed to send file data
/note/{noteID} GET noteID <string> Query 200 title <string>, content <string>, tags <string[]> Constantly get new file content from server for live rendering
/note/{noteID} GET noteID <string> Query 404 Error <string> File not found, failed to fetch
/note/{noteID1}
/{noteID2}		 PUT linedNotes <string[]> Body 200 Link two notes
/note/{noteID1}
/{noteID2}		 PUT linedNotes <string[]> Body 404 Failed to link notes
/link POST noteID1 <string>, noteID2 <string> Body 201 Link two notes (alternative option)
/link POST noteID1 <string>, noteID2 <string> Body 404 Failed to link notes
/user/{userID} PUT accessableNotes <string[]> Body 200 Give read/write permissions to user
/user/{userID} PUT accessableNotes <string[]> Body 404 Failed to give permissions
/files POST vault <string[]>,
folderStructure <Tree>		 Body 201 Create new vault
/files POST vault <string[]>,
folderStructure <Tree>		 Body 409 Failed to create new vault
/cursors/{noteID} PUT cursorPos <(float, float)> Body 200 Send cursor position to server
/cursors/{noteID} PUT cursorPos <(float, float)> Body 409 Failed to send cursor position
/database/{noteID} GET noteID <string> Query 200 title <string>, content <string>, tags <string[]> Getting the latest version of the document
/database/{noteID} GET noteID <string> Query 404 Error <string> Failed to fetch note version
/user/{userID} POST username <string>, email <string> Body 201 Create new user
/user/{userID} POST username <string>, email <string> Body 409 User already exists
/user/{userID} PUT status <string> Body 200 Update user status
/user/{userID} PUT status <string> Body 404 User not found
/note/{noteID} POST title <string>, content <string>, tags <string[]> Body 201 Create new note / vault
/note/{noteID} POST title <string>, content <string>, tags <string[]> Body    409
